text: Just sent an email, but noted that vroom site is down. Anything we can do?
There isn't.
This is unfortunately the work of the iffy drupal production partner they chose.

Texted Bezos. Her response:

"No apologies necessary (for early text). I have reason to believe it's been down for some days :( I was in E. Wa this weekend, and I thought it was my connection. Came back to town late last night, and realized it wasn't just me."
Vroom site appears to be back online.
From their latest email, unsure of how DNS changed, other than that their ELB address was reallocated.
